OL,4,CCovid: One in five firms plan job cuts
OL,5,Cas furlough tapers - survey
OL,6, One in five firms plan on letting staff
OL,7, go in response to Sunday's furlough
OL,8, policy change, which will see employers
OL,9, contribute more, a survey has found.
OL,11,FThe British Chamber of Commerce said
OL,12,Fextra training was needed to deal with
OL,13,Fthousands of redundancies predicted.
OL,15,FFrom Sunday, government payments reduce
OL,16,Fto 60% towards salaries, with employers
OL,17,Fpaying 20%.
OL,19,FThe government said the approach was
OL,20,F"right" and meant "we can focus support
OL,21,Felsewhere" as the economy recovers.
